Package: MMimmuneRisk
Title: Immune-Related Risk Classifier for Multiple Myeloma
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: person("HXE", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "hxe@example.com")
Description: A machine-learning-based risk stratification tool for multiple myeloma
    patients using immune-related gene expression. Implements a RSF + plsRcox pipeline
    to compute a Programmed Cell Death Index (PCDI) risk score from bulk RNA-seq data,
    classifies patients into High/Low risk groups, and provides a dynamic nomogram
    (Shiny app) for individualized survival prediction.
